  "text": "The basic data of morphological traits for definition of leaf life dynamics were extracted from dynamic MTGs under AMAPStudio [CITATION_1] , differentiating the period (active and reduced vegetative growth) of metamer appearance, leaf growth and fall, and order of axis supporter (first to fifth). In dynamic MTGs, each axis had the attributed identification that allowed the extraction of its components relative to sequential dates.",
